column5: I delivered the 3rd Salmon Aquarium & Cooler/Chiller to the Walkerton Catholic High School today with the Salmon to be Delivered on Friday hopefully, I was at the Kincardine Hatchery on Sunday & the Brown Trout have hatched & the Rainbows are growing everything looks great to me. Thank a Volunteer next time you see one Thanx & Tight Lines Richard  http://lhfcschoolhat...s.blogspot.com/
Great stuff. Hats off to the guys and gals that put in time at that great little hatchery!!
